1. Set the build environment: source poky/oe-init-build-env ; cd ..
2. Set the layer for the image to be stored in
  1. Create a layer: bitbake-layers create-layer meta-[name]
  2. Add the layer: Open `build/conf/bblayers.conf` and add [root]/meta-[name]
3. Create an image directory in the layer: mkdir -p [root]/meta-[name]/recipes-core/images
4. Create ypdd-image.bb in this directory and write the recipe in it
5. Build the image: bitbake -k ypdd-image
6. Run the image: runqemu qemux86-64
